{"title":"Serratia marcescens-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/Serratia marcescens-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Serratia\\Nmarcescens","guid":"v25P6Eafr5sbE2sMTRBXPw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Contexto Clínico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Causa infecciones locales y sistémicas en hospedadores normales e inmunocomprometidos.","guid":"ByXjkCUGVOTvBf38DOfOAA","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Aumento en la prevalencia de cepas multirresistentes (MDR).","guid":"lStGAsnsW65inYSkufP_Bg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"• Mecanismos de resistencia: ESBL, AmpC, carbapenemasas (serinas y metaloenzimas), resistencia a\\Naminoglucósidos (enzimas modificadoras, baja permeabilidad de la pared celular, bombas de eflujo).","guid":"VwP9tCwZXjuInI0u-y2Msw","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"• Bacilos Gram-negativos facultativos aerobios.","guid":"yQLMeHUI0S53GAeip1mppA","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Regímenes\\NPrimarios","guid":"nkYMMsVetF6hXuzJrIFbnA","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"1. Empírico (Resistencia\\Nlocal <15%)","guid":"RHfanMmyex8Lis113xA4Nw","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"• Piperacilina-tazobactam: 4.5 g IV carga → 3.375 g IV c/8h (↑ dosis si IMC ≥30).","guid":"9UJj89BkzX8cSAM_0d60ZQ","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"• Ceftriaxona: 1-2 g IV c/24h.","guid":"aIyciLOajZ-KMPw4gmsVuQ","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"• Aztreonam: 2 g IV c/8h.","guid":"wZbEZKR5oHr8IXY84-YvCA","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"8","text":"• Ciprofloxacina: 400 mg IV c/12h.","guid":"qD6G7bCMRC6ULQAtZSX6iQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"8","text":"• Levofloxacina: 750 mg IV c/24h.","guid":"rwUPA_WNfPOOc9Yp9YurPQ","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"8","text":"• Cefepima: 1-2 g IV c/8-12h.","guid":"5JQGnMVz7U-IgEL7KG7qKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"7","text":"2. Empírico (Resistencia\\Nlocal >15%)","guid":"dr2tNZgXu3S7PNA59L0jCg","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"• Meropenem: 1-2 g IV c/8h.","guid":"aKK6Q7MFIMsN3QiUoiCCTA","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"• Ertapenem: 1 g IV c/24h.","guid":"OAwuAB7_nVvuEcoU14zoaQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"0","text":"Resistencia\\NIdentificada","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"• ESBL y/o AmpC: Cefepima preferible en infecciones de alto inóculo.","guid":"hS6NCVLHCh9O-1pyi6WXfQ","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"• Carbapenemasas de serina (KPC): Meropenem-vaborbactam, ceftazidima-avibactam.","guid":"Kg7pAijHKqQ98dxnEpp40w","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"• Metalo-beta-lactamasas: Ceftazidima-avibactam + aztreonam, cefiderocol.","guid":"Vs_ChaOSm8rgkuDKJWj41A","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"Resistencia Intrínseca","guid":"","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• Polimixinas, ampicilina, cefazolina, nitrofurantoína.","guid":"wj6ReZST0SWoAchSe_AQ7Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"• Alergia a beta-lactámicos:\\NCiprofloxacina, aztreonam, gentamicina.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"• Antimicrobial Stewardship:\\NEvitar uso innecesario de\\Npolimixinas y carbapenémicos.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"0","text":"Consultas\\NEspecializadas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• Recomendación de consulta a\\Ninfectología para infecciones\\Ngraves o panresistentes.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Clin Infect Dis\\N2019; 68:519.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"• Antimicrob Agents Chemother.\\N2019; 63:e01551-18.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"• IDSA Guideline 2023: Clin Infect\\NDis. 2023 Jul 18:ciad428.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":32,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Infectología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Infectología","filename":"Serratia marcescens-2024","id":"map_1179","resolved_references":[]}